This is one of the good places in Brooklyn where you can find good pub food, beer, and catch up with some of your favorite sports team on the big screen. I’ve tried one of their famous BBQ wing dish, which was infused with rum, and the taste was pretty unique, not your average BBQ wings for sure! Verdict: it was simply delicious, and you can definitely taste the rum. Prices are not that bad, and there are plenty of draft beers to choose from. A few more tables would be good tough, since this place does get crowded at times.
